    </div>
    <p style="margin:2rem 0 0; padding-top:1.25rem; border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); font-size:0.72rem; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3); display:flex; justify-content:space-between; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:0.5rem;">
      <span>&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} Wild Roots Native Gardens · Earth-first since 2015</span>
